## 卸载
```bash
# 停止服务
sudo /opt/AdGuardHome/AdGuardHome -s stop
sudo /opt/AdGuardHome/AdGuardHome -s uninstall

# 删除文件
sudo rm -rf /opt/AdGuardHome

# 恢复 DNS 设置
echo "nameserver 1.1.1.1" | sudo tee /etc/resolv.conf
```

